安慰剂告诉批评者对圣加仑节日的抱怨要“过上生活”和“有远见” https://www.nme.com/news/music/placebo-tell-critics-to-get-a-life-and-a-sense-of-perspective-over-st-gallen-festival-complaints-3773049？ utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=安慰剂告诉批评者在圣加仑节日投诉上获得生活和视角Surej SinghTue, 09 Jul 2024 04:02:25 +0000 Music NewsNewsIndieRock https://www.nme.com/?p=3773049 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/placebo@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Placebo 将于 2024 年现场表演" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/placebo@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/placebo@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/placebo@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/placebo@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/placebo@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/placebo@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “安慰剂在舞台上不使用任何录音。一切都是 100% 现场直播”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/placebo-tell-critics-to-get-a-life-and-a-sense-of-perspective-over-st-gallen-festival-complaints-3773049">《Placebo》的帖子告诉批评者对圣加仑音乐节的抱怨要“重获生活”和“有远见”，该帖子</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/placebo@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Placebo 将于 2024 年现场表演" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/placebo@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/placebo@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/placebo@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/placebo@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/placebo@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/placebo@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>在乐队最近在圣加仑音乐节演出中因技术问题而受到批评后， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/placebo">Placebo</a>针对批评者发表了一份声明 - 看看乐队在下面怎么说。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/placebo-never-let-me-go-david-bowie-brian-molko-stefan-olsdal-intervew-3181905">安慰剂：“大卫·鲍伊教我如何成为一个更好的人”</a></strong></li></ul><p> 6 月 30 日，Placebo 被预订在瑞士圣加仑露天音乐节上与 Chainsmokers 和 Queens Of The Stone Age 等乐队一起演出。在演出期间，乐队遇到了一些技术问题，迫使乐队缩短了演出时间，结束时间比预期早得多。</p><p>从那时起，乐队的表演和歌迷内部的争斗一直受到批评，促使乐队的布莱恩·莫尔科在社交媒体上发表声明。莫尔科开始说道：“我们注意到我们的歌迷之间就圣加仑音乐节被缩短的音乐会进行了大量的讨论、争论、指责和小冲突。我们还收到了许多（缺乏想象力且有权利的）侮辱。因此，我们想澄清一下圣加仑音乐节音乐会期间发生的事情。” </p><figure id="attachment_3773053" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3773053" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3773053" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/placebo-stefan@2000x1270.jpg" alt="安慰剂的斯特凡·奥尔斯达尔" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/placebo-stefan@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/placebo-stefan@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/placebo-stefan@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/placebo-stefan@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/placebo-stefan@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/placebo-stefan@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3773053" class="wp-caption-text">安慰剂的斯特凡·奥尔斯达尔。图片来源：ANNA KURTH/法新社，盖蒂图片社</figcaption></figure><p>“演出开始不久，Stefan [Olsdal] 就开始出现技术问题，直到吉他系统最终完全停止工作。所以他再也不能用吉他弹奏任何歌曲了。我们世界一流的船员尽一切努力来解决这个问题，但没有效果。”</p><p>布莱恩·莫尔科 (Brian Molko) 解释说，乐队决定不走下舞台，而是决定与斯特凡 (Stefan) 弹奏贝斯，尽其所能地演奏。他还承认乐队确保向出席的观众解释发生了什么。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C9K8W3lNMxU/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.886,58.899 532.1,66.113 541,66.113 C549.9,66.113 557.115,58.899 557.115,50 C557.115,41.1 549.9,33.886 541,33.886 M565.378,62.101 C565.244,65.022 564.756,66.606 564.346,67.663 C563.8